----- stdout -----
Generate financial reports

Usage: borrow-checker report [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  net-worth  Net worth across all asset and liability accounts
  monthly    Monthly income and expense summary
  annual     Annual summary broken down by month
  budget     Budget vs actuals (requires Milestone 5)
  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --json               Emit machine-readable JSON instead of human-readable output [env: BC_JSON=]
      --db-path <DB_PATH>  Path to the SQLite database file [env: BC_DB_PATH=[TEMP_DIR]/test.db]
  -h, --help               Print help
